data.meta_description: Donald Gordon CHAPMAN was born on August 28, 1928 in Queensland, Australia, son of Albert Hall CHAPMAN and Alice Mary BARR. He was married on March 10, 1951 in Queensland, Australia to (Not public). He died on February  6, 1991 in Ayr, Queensland, Australia. This information is part of Tangeman Genealogy by Margaret Paret on Genealogy Online.
